FBIS4-9339 "dreeu079_k_94001" FBIS-EEU-94-079 Daily Report 25 Apr 1994 CROATIA Akashi Postpones Meeting With Krajina President Akashi Postpones Meeting With Krajina President LD2504095494 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service in Serbo-Croatian 0916 GMT 25 Apr 94 LD2504095494 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service Serbo-Croatian BFN [Text] Knin, 25 Apr (TANJUG) -- UN special envoy Yasushi Akashi's meeting with Krajina's state leadership and President Milan Martic, scheduled for today, has been postpone at Akashi's request. In a message to President Martic, Akashi says he has had to postpone the meeting due to his tasks in connection with monitoring the situation in Bosnia.
